a"], "date": "1914-01-30", "dates": ["1914-01-30"], "description": ["tr I T X Y V X r t i Piedmont Quality means Highest Quality Unchang ing Quality Year after year the same ripe mellow tobacco the same perfect workmanship the same pleasure end satis faction Imitators have despaired of ever equalling Piedmont Quality Whole coupon in each package lOIarJ I SPECIAL WINTER MILLINERY Until February 1st In order to reduce our large stock of Winter Millinery we will until the above date sell at greatly reduced prices our entire line Every item in the store is of thfe latest design no old stock Such a reduction in prices at this season has never been attempt ed Inf Ocala before Call and see for yourself Mss M Commercial Bank Building W H MARSH Phone 108 The Y T Y Laundry That Made Ocala Famous I Y 402404 S VULCANIZING We are equipped with the Latest Largest Best Vulcanizing plant in Central Florida Any sized tire handled at one time AU work Guaranteed to e FirstClass Bring us your Casings and Tubes to be Vulcanized Worn out tires and tubes Jought FISK and FIRESTONE TIRES of all sizes and rims always in stock DA VIES The Tire Man Phone 438 OCALA"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-01-27T16:57:47.864Z", "group": ["ndnp/fu", "university-of-florida-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84027621/1914-01-30/ed-1/?sp=5", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_beaty_ver01:data:sn84027621:00295865908:1914013001:0198/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=286&w=208", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_beaty_ver01:data:sn84027621:00295865908:1914013001:0198/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=572&w=416", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_beaty_ver01:data:sn84027621:00295865908:1914013001:0198/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1144&w=833", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/fu/batch_fu_beaty_ver01/data/sn84